summary: This is an email from an unknown sender to the FBI New York field office, dated September 20, 2021, with the subject line referencing photos and containing two image attachments named 'edinburgh.jpg' and 'a_going_awayparty.jpg'. The document is part of the Epstein case data set and appears to be a submission of potential evidence.

events.title: Email Submission to FBI NY
events.description: An email was sent to the FBI New York field office with the subject '[EXTERNAL EMAIL] - photo's' and two attached image files.

keyFacts: An email was sent to the FBI New York field office on September 20, 2021, regarding photos.
The email contained two image attachments: 'edinburgh.jpg' and 'a_going_awayparty.jpg'.
The subject line suggests the email was an external submission, potentially from a member of the public or a source.
